{"tid":89927,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果正式起訴高通","createTime":"2017-01-21T16:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T16:01:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df476e7c19d31f73abdd68a37be89d2948566484","tid":89927,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"蘋果正式起訴高通：把你答應退還的 10 億美元專利費退給我！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.techbang.com/posts/48961-apple-formally-charged-qualcomm-patent-fees-you-agreed-to-refund-1-billion-back-to-me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F48961-apple-formally-charged-qualcomm-patent-fees-you-agreed-to-refund-1-billion-back-to-me&d=F77gZwdEA7vBqSzj0okTB6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=f8df30f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.techbang.com/posts/48961-apple-formally-charged-qualcomm-patent-fees-you-agreed-to-refund-1-billion-back-to-me</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1-techbang.pixcdn.tw/system/excerpt_images/48961/inpage/e0829eb7553bd3c5a0a2218d1c109215.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1-techbang.pixcdn.tw%2Fsystem%2Fexcerpt_images%2F48961%2Finpage%2Fe0829eb7553bd3c5a0a2218d1c109215.png&h=f7e88984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 1 月 17 日，美國聯邦貿易協會（Federal Trade Comission，以下簡稱FTC）起訴高通強迫蘋果進行獨家交易以購買其繫帶晶片，當蘋果尋求降低支付給高通的專利使用費時，高通以此作為條件要求蘋果在 2011 年和 2016 年期間獨家購買高通的晶片。<br />\n<br />\n日前蘋果也正式發起了對高通的訴訟，表示高通非法利用手機晶片領域的壟斷地位，要求高通退還 10 億美元曾經承諾退還的專利使用費。蘋果在聲明中指出，高通為了報復蘋果與 FTC 的合作，非法扣留了原本承諾退還的 10 億美元專利使用費用。並且表示：<br />\n<br />\n多年來，高通一直以在不公平的方式來收取與他們沒關係的技術專利費用。蘋果在 Touch ID、顯示螢幕、相機等方面的創新越多，高通所收購的專利費用就高，而且是毫無理由的。對於蘋果來說，創新之路也就變得越來越昂貴。雖然高通只是這一行資料標準的眾多貢獻者之一，但他們向蘋果收取的費用，是其它授權者向蘋果收費總和的至少五倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ifanr-cdn.b0.upaiyun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/AppleA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fifanr-cdn.b0.upaiyun.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FAppleA9.jpg&h=f243ab7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管蘋果 A 系列處理器一直可以算得上是性能最優異的處理器之一，但是由於蘋果缺少行動網路方面的專利，所以在處理器的通訊繫帶上，主要使用的是高通的 MDM ，同時蘋果也是高通的第一大客戶。不過目前蘋果與高通的獨家協議已經到期，iPhone 7 這一代產品中，蘋果在使用高通產品的同時，也使用了英特爾的產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ifanr-cdn.b0.upaiyun.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/qualcomm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fifanr-cdn.b0.upaiyun.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fqualcomm.jpg&h=f8b3c8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高通的壟斷問題顯然已經引起了多方關注，2015年2月，在經歷14個月的調查後，高通在中國支付了9.75億美元的罰款，並被責令調整專利授權模式。同年12月，歐盟也指控高通濫用市場地位，打壓競爭對手。上個月，韓國反壟斷監管機構宣佈對高通開出約 58.6 億元人民幣罰單，原因是其專利許可協議觸犯了反壟斷法律法規。而對於高通來說，蘋果和三星業務佔到高通營收的近半壁江山，上一財年高通營收為 1614 億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n在專利使用的收費方案上，高通通常會打包向客戶授權專利，即使客戶只會使用到高通很少的技術。手機廠商需要向高通繳納相當於手機售價 5% 左右的專利使用費。在遭到韓國政府起訴時高通解釋稱：其創新推動了行動通信的爆炸性增長，惠及業內其他廠商。它指出，對於手機和晶片廠商來說，其打包許可策略是划算的，按零件計算專利使用費會進一步上漲，所以自家多年來一直以打包方式對外許可專利。"},{"pid":"fd2736b82c2a911eb6029005f64b2f11c8bf380c","tid":89927,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"打完齋就唔要和尚，蘋果真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a705ee0f3746746b78f192327fd2c64924869c7","tid":89927,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:16:46.000Z","msg":"台灣新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfef9e3e2a37769ec873863e861c49e6819c6e1","tid":89927,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T19:51:57.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049898c7e313549cfee3c8547fa279baf368020f","tid":89927,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b759c649c3d60457cd7aa07432a24b9a204decaa","tid":89927,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打完齋就唔要和尚，蘋果真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去驗眼啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb925e9c19d6daa47da5d9894e218e06d779a28a","tid":89927,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打完齋就唔要和尚，蘋果真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去驗眼啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗撚驗眼咩, 佢地班信徒睇到就夠. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25091549542c38a99a46e94c5731e9a66080bfb7","tid":89927,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9d814bb020c66ac24e6a84b5cc5ec272df8818","tid":89927,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貼返香港篇報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2017/01/apple-sues-qualcomm-for-shady-business/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2017%2F01%2Fapple-sues-qualcomm-for-shady-business%2F&d=F77gZwdEA7vBqSzj0okTB6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=3cd89bb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2017/01/apple-sues-qualcomm-for-shady-business/</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果怒告Qualcomm　　稱他們亂收錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/qualcomm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fqualcomm.jpg&h=949dde9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQualcomm生產的數據機是不少手機的重要零件之一，蘋果最近卻忍不住控告他們，原因之一是因為Qualcomm的經營生意的手法令蘋果不滿。據稱，他們最近扣留了蘋果就購買Qualcomm專利權的費用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果表示，其實有不少公司都有就基本的通訊技術作出努力，可是Qualcomm卻堅持要向他們收取多達五倍的專利授權費用。蘋果更怒稱Qualcomm經常就一些與他們無關的技術而收費，蘋果發明的Touch ID、相機、更佳的螢幕等，都無緣無故地令Qualcomm賺更多的錢。蘋果今次控告中，希望爭取高達US$10億的賠償。<br />\n<br />\n來源：TNW、CNBC"},{"pid":"2cd5a48d65bb17be054962c64f237f6fe4c433df","tid":89927,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"咁係要買專利喎"},{"pid":"2d8fbef7573d0c2f97ef41fbd6cef6e44afa8528","tid":89927,"uid":7886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"蘋果呢隻專利流氓夠膽死話鳩通<br />\niPhone 7 一用Intel 即刻出事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54b38260bd333d63ec7268ce0aab7e6be6932d3","tid":89927,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蘋果呢隻專利流氓夠膽死話鳩通<br />\niPhone 7 一用Intel 即刻出事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係你支持鳩通繼續壟斷市場？"}]}